## 🎨 Customization

### Changing Colors
Edit `styles.py` and modify the color values in the CSS:
```python
# Primary color
background-color: #2E86AB;  # Change this

# Secondary color  
border-left: 4px solid #A23B72;  # Change this
```

### Adding New Interview Types
Edit `config.py`:
```python
INTERVIEW_MODES = [
    "Technical Interview",
    "Behavioral Interview",
    "Your New Type",  # Add here
]
```

### Creating Custom Prompts
Edit `prompts.py` and add your prompt to `SYSTEM_PROMPTS` dictionary.

